SQL query of the view VCMM_CMM_COMENTARIO_MIGRADO

SELECT ENU_ID, CON_ID, MCS.MCS_ID, MCS.MCS_CD_TIPO, MCS.MCS_CD_CNPJ, MCS.MCS_NM_IF, MCS.MCS_CD_BLOQUEADO, MCS.MCS_SQ, MCS.MCS_DT_DATA_BASE, MCS.MCS_DS_DEPARTAMENTO, MCS.MCS_NU_NOTA, MCS.MCS_NM_ULTIMO_TITULO_ADITADO, MCS.MCS_NM_INSERIDOR, MCS.MCS_NM_INSERIDOR_CARGO, MCS.MCS_DT_INSERIDOR_DATA, MCS.MCS_NM_ELABORADOR,MCS.MCS_NM_ELABORADOR_EQUIPE,MCS.MCS_NM_ELABORADOR_CARGO, MCS.MCS_DT_ELABORADOR_DATA, MCS.MCS_NM_ATIVIDADE, MCS.MCS_DT_ULTIMO_ADITAMENTO, MCS.MCS_DH_ATUALZ, CMM.CMM_ID, CMM.CMM_AN_CORPO,CMM.CMM_AN_CABECALHO, CMM.CMM_CD_BLOQUEADO, CMM.CMM_DH_ATUALZ,CMM.CMM_CD_OPER_ATUALZ,CMM.CMM_NU_VERSAO, ECM_DS AS ECM_DS_CNPJS FROM SUP.MCS_METADADOS_COMENTARIO_SISCOMENT MCS INNER JOIN SUP.CMM_COMENTARIO_MIGRADO CMM ON MCS.CMM_ID = CMM.CMM_ID INNER JOIN SUP.ECM_EVENTOS_COMENTARIO_MIGRADO ECM ON ECM.CMM_ID = CMM.CMM_ID INNER JOIN SUP.EVC_EVENTO_CONSOLIDADO EVC ON EVC.EVC_ID = ECM.EVC_ID WHERE MCS.MCS_CD_TIPO IN (1,2) AND (MCS.MCS_DT_INSERIDOR_DATA >= '2015-01-01' AND MCS.MCS_DT_INSERIDOR_DATA < '2018-01-01')
